# Heroku Procfile — `staffler-poc-api` (Option C in DEPLOY.md).
#
# `web` is the only process type the API app needs:
#   - Fastify listens on $PORT (Heroku injects it)
#   - serves /api/* (proxy to Staffler gateway, with session cookies)
#
# The Angular SPA + MyStaffler PWA are deployed as sister apps
# (staffler-poc-web, staffler-mystaffler) using the static buildpack —
# this dyno does NOT serve any frontend.
#
# Bumping to two dynos (web + worker) lands here when we add background
# jobs like FCM token cleanup or daily seedDemo refreshes. Not yet.
#
# Migrations: `release` runs once on every deploy before the new `web`
# starts taking traffic — perfect for the Postgres schema apply.
release: node scripts/migrate.mjs
web: node dist/server/index.js
